description:
MindCrack is a server Guude started in late 2010. It is a private (whitelisted) server. We are currently not accepting applications. 

Here's a little update to what I've been up to on the server. I also decide to give Guude a nice present he's always wanted.

Guude's Present Reaction:
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YJ0jJxUTtH0

When opening the gift he did not realize, or even consider, that the records were actually legitimate dungeon records because they are so impossible to get. I told him afterwards.

Video of me hanging out with BdoubleO:
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qxKEG5-OQz4
